"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"In our daily life, some people are unfortunate to lose their sight, lose their hearing, and so on. Be the disabled, they lead a very hard life, but they still struggle to keep alive. We should not turn our backs on them. Instead, we are supposed to give them a hand. In order to make disabled people’s life much easier and more convenient, we can help them by doing some little things, such as, offering our seats to them on the bus, showing them the right way on the road, leading them across the street, and so on. If all of us can offer our love and show our warmth to the disabled, our world will be more beautiful and harmonious. \\n  \\n 在我们的日常生活中，有些人不幸失去了他们的视力，失去了他们的听力等。作为残疾人，他们过着非常艰苦的生活，但他们仍在为生存而努力。我们不应该嫌弃他们。相反，我们应该帮助他们。为了使残疾人的生活更容易和更方便，我们可以通过做一些小事来帮助他们，例如，在公共汽车上给他们让座，在路上给他们指明正确的方向，带领他们过马路等。如果我们人人都能给他们一点爱、一点温暖，我们的世界将会更加美丽、和谐。\",\"timestamp\":1634968067,\"title\":\"Don’t ignore the disabled\"},\"digest\":\"S7KbuP1OehThsntoqHfRuzrGIt3XxdtvYIT-Tp7_Pwk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAe401639475397d34CEcfF48BaedDd03358b5cB2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8sZQ36wJkasjE5tBuZKIrOyASnMfqN6ZfhA7Ze3sb4g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"a8NwmGJw8NZqRlLTmCF_EFNxSqSBW-GmFDm-FsPOKGA\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lHGxaZBMcwsrgsdapljfaYVi3YXc0TCLl9pJPQPleJiqh0dcuzcbzBBdCWA7bAy0yndO4E9ihf32u6xSKCr0WA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x3878e60eb60e3e6940dfa899eee1cb8b0057451882e6548e059b88ecf7d6c9b03132085d7e89957f68673ed503a6ef8cde2862920874e0cf5dbb1b992449d25d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"8sZQ36wJkasjE5tBuZKIrOyASnMfqN6ZfhA7Ze3sb4g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"a8NwmGJw8NZqRlLTmCF_EFNxSqSBW-GmFDm-FsPOKGA\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalD